  "detailed_description": "<h1>Check my New Game!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I’m excited to introduce my new game: <strong>Midnight Billiards</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/923222c6ad07e4c5425b11c8ec93016e.avif?t=1764693750\" width=800 height=450 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s a <strong>roguelike</strong> that combines <strong>billiards</strong> and <strong>pinball</strong>, delivering fast-paced and chilling gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I’m sure you’ll love it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find it on my homepage!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Arrive in Time\" is a minimalist casual strategy game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your goal is to drive a car and collect stars within the time limit to pass each level.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >119 different levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Estimated playtime: 4-8 hours</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >support keyboard&mouse and controller</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gradual difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minimalist, relaxed vibe</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Simple Controls</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are only two types of actions in the game: pressing the gas pedal and using cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can play the entire game using just one mouse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/820152c308be42cd26d3767342b8d7bf.poster.avif?t=1764693750\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/820152c308be42cd26d3767342b8d7bf.webm?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/820152c308be42cd26d3767342b8d7bf.mp4?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Using Cards</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use cards to turn left, turn right, or accelerate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Timing is crucial, so don't waste any card.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress through the game, you'll acquire more cards and items to help you solve puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/3f36b3edb6e84fb977f65b73cb25cf0b.poster.avif?t=1764693750\" width=480 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/3f36b3edb6e84fb977f65b73cb25cf0b.webm?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/3f36b3edb6e84fb977f65b73cb25cf0b.mp4?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Follow the Rules</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't crash into other cars or people, and obey the rules.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features various obstacles that players need to navigate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you advance through levels, more new mechanics will be introduced.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/e8620d978ed3a908545df3b4a56b0270.poster.avif?t=1764693750\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/e8620d978ed3a908545df3b4a56b0270.webm?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/e8620d978ed3a908545df3b4a56b0270.mp4?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Beware of Night Driving</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's said that in some areas, drivers become tense when driving at night—to the point of losing consciousness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So, try to stay in well-lit areas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perhaps buying a \"Ghost Detector\" from the shop might help you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/600a67c8f2d35bb522ad1cdd262cd47b.poster.avif?t=1764693750\" width=480 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/600a67c8f2d35bb522ad1cdd262cd47b.webm?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/600a67c8f2d35bb522ad1cdd262cd47b.mp4?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Arrive in Time\" is a minimalist casual strategy game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your goal is to drive a car and collect stars within the time limit to pass each level.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >119 different levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Estimated playtime: 4-8 hours</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >support keyboard&mouse and controller</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gradual difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minimalist, relaxed vibe</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Simple Controls</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are only two types of actions in the game: pressing the gas pedal and using cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can play the entire game using just one mouse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/820152c308be42cd26d3767342b8d7bf.poster.avif?t=1764693750\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/820152c308be42cd26d3767342b8d7bf.webm?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/820152c308be42cd26d3767342b8d7bf.mp4?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Using Cards</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use cards to turn left, turn right, or accelerate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Timing is crucial, so don't waste any card.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress through the game, you'll acquire more cards and items to help you solve puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/3f36b3edb6e84fb977f65b73cb25cf0b.poster.avif?t=1764693750\" width=480 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/3f36b3edb6e84fb977f65b73cb25cf0b.webm?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/3f36b3edb6e84fb977f65b73cb25cf0b.mp4?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Follow the Rules</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't crash into other cars or people, and obey the rules.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features various obstacles that players need to navigate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you advance through levels, more new mechanics will be introduced.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/e8620d978ed3a908545df3b4a56b0270.poster.avif?t=1764693750\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/e8620d978ed3a908545df3b4a56b0270.webm?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/e8620d978ed3a908545df3b4a56b0270.mp4?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Beware of Night Driving</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's said that in some areas, drivers become tense when driving at night—to the point of losing consciousness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So, try to stay in well-lit areas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perhaps buying a \"Ghost Detector\" from the shop might help you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/600a67c8f2d35bb522ad1cdd262cd47b.poster.avif?t=1764693750\" width=480 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/600a67c8f2d35bb522ad1cdd262cd47b.webm?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/600a67c8f2d35bb522ad1cdd262cd47b.mp4?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
